definition: Fen River
name of a river
river/CL:條|条[tiao2],道[dao4]

sentences.english: East Fen River in the east coast, Ming Chen Li, deputy Zhenguan presided over the building.
sentences.chinese: 东城在汾河东岸，为贞观名臣李副主持修筑。

sentences.english: Furthermore, the practical calculations are processed by the temperature data of natural ice in second reservoir of Taiyuan fen-river.
sentences.chinese: 利用太原汾河二库天然冰温度场数据进行了实际计算。

sentences.english: Fenhe Second reservoir has not been formed the eutrophication.
sentences.chinese: 汾河二库尚未形成富营养化状态。

sentences.english: The basic characteristics of the soil seed bank in flood plain grassland of the Fen River in Taiyuan region were investigated and studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了汾河太原段河漫滩草地土壤种子库的基本特征。

sentences.english: To know about the eutrophic condition of present Fenhe Second reservoir.
sentences.chinese: 了解汾河二库水体现阶段的富营养状况。

sentences.english: The Shanxi plain is watered by the Fen River which runs through it.
sentences.chinese: 山西平元由流经这里的汾河灌溉。
